NETHERLANDS COASTGUARD
NAVIGATIONAL WARNING - ADDITIONAL NR. 86 010312 UTC JAN
WAVE HEIGHT WARNING 300CM TSS TERSCHELLING - GERMAN BIGHT
ISSUED AT 010300 UTC JAN
CONTAINER VESSELS WITH A LENGTH OF 100-200M ARE AT RISK
OF LOSING CONTAINERS DURING HEAVY SEA CONDITIONS
IN PARTICULAR FROM A WEST-NORTHWEST TO NORTHERLY DIRECTION.
THESE VESSELS SHOULD ALTER COURSE IF NECESSARY TO AVOID
COMING ABEAM TO THE WAVES AND TAKE OTHER APPROPRIATE MEASURES
TO AVOID LOSING CONTAINERS.
